{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/WEB/stroage-cookie","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"2aa43805-2e5b-5f2e-88d3-7646586bbda2","html":"<h1 id=\"스토리지와-쿠키\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A7%80%EC%99%80-%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%A4\" aria-label=\"스토리지와 쿠키 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>스토리지와 쿠키</h1>\n<p>클라이언트 정보를 저장하는 역할은 크게 스토리지와 쿠키가 있다.\n스토리지와 쿠키는 key, value 쌍으로 저장된다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"1-스토리지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"1 스토리지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 스토리지</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>영구성에 따라 로컬 스토리지와 세션 스토리지로 구분된다.</li>\n<li>사용자 웹브라우저측에 있는 저장소</li>\n<li>쿠키에 비해 용량이 크다.</li>\n<li>매번 서버로 보내지지 않아서 경제적이고 보안성이 높음</li>\n<li>도메인마다 저장소가 별도(같은 도메인 내에서는 같은 데이터에 접근할 수 있음)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"로컬-스토리지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A1%9C%EC%BB%AC-%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"로컬 스토리지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>로컬 스토리지</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>강제로 지우지 않으면 계속 브라우저에 남아있다.</li>\n<li>로그인, 설정 데이터 등을 저장</li>\n<li>세팅방법</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'heejin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nlocalStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'heejin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>값 가져오기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nlocalStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 값이 없을 경우</span>\nlocalStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'not_exist'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nlocalStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>not_exist<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>삭제</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"세션-스토리지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%B8%EC%85%98-%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"세션 스토리지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>세션 스토리지</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>브라우저가 닫히면 없어진다.</li>\n<li>간단한 입력폼 정보를 저장</li>\n<li>세팅방법</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">sessionStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'heejin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nsessionStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'heejin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>값 가져오기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">sessionStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nsessionStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 값이 없을 경우</span>\nsessionStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'not_exist'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nsessionStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>not_exist<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>삭제</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">sessionStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"2-쿠키\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%A4\" aria-label=\"2 쿠키 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 쿠키</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>개인 맞춤 서비스 제공, 방문/이용 형태, 인기검색어, 보안접속여부 파악 등을 위해 웹서버가 방문자의 컴퓨터에 설치하는 작은 정보 파일</li>\n<li>이용자에 의해 조회·수정(변조)·삭제될 수 있음</li>\n<li>보안상 중요한 정보를 담아두면 안됨</li>\n<li>자동로그인, 팝업에서 “오늘 더 이상 이 창을 보지 않음” 체크, 쇼핑몰의 장바구니 저장</li>\n<li>4KB의 작은 저장소</li>\n<li>세팅방법</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">setCookie</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'heejin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>값 가져오기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">getCookie</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>삭제</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">deleteCookie</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/WEB/stroage-cookie","tagSlugs":["/tag/web/","/tag/stroage/","/tag/cookie/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-03-27","description":"stroage, cookie","tags":["web","stroage","cookie"],"title":"stroage, cookie","socialImage":"/media/42-line-bible.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/WEB/stroage-cookie"}}}